cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.GR 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with super-resolution using deep convolutional neural networks. It also involves neural architecture search, which falls under the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The use of evolutionary computation and reinforcement learning suggests it could also belong to the neural networks (cs.NE) sub-category. Finally, the proposed elastic search tactic could be related to the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category.
